UINT16 Media::Parameters::frame_rate_denominator
 

Frame rate denominator. Actual frame rate (in frames/sec) is calculated as m_frame_rate_numerator/m_frame_rate_denominator.

UINT16 Media::Parameters::frame_rate_numerator
 

Frame rate numerator. Actual frame rate (in frames/sec) is calculated as m_frame_rate_numerator/m_frame_rate_denominator.
